quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  70,36,Femalilleziyne keferu kﾄｱbeleke muhtﾄｱﾂｴﾄｱyne
  70,37,Anilyemiyni ve ﾂｴaniﾅ淒殃mali ﾂｴﾄｱziyne
  70,38,Eyatmeﾂｴu kullumriin minhum en yudhale cennete naﾂｴﾄｱymin
  70,39,Kella inna halaknahum mimma yaﾂｴlemune
  70,40,Fela uksimu birabbilmeﾅ歛rikﾄｱ velmeﾄ歛ribi inna likadirune
  70,41,Ala en nubeddile hayren minhum ve ma nahnu bimesbukﾄｱyne
  70,42,Fezerhum yehudu ve yelﾂｴadune
  70,43,Yevme yahrucune minelﾂｴecdasi siraﾂｴan keennehum ila nusubin yufidune
  70,44,Haﾅ殃ﾂｴaten ebsaruhum terhekuhum zilletun zalikelyevmulleziy kanu yuﾂｴadune